-- Sample roads (links)
-- frc: Functional Road Class (0-7, 0 being highest)
-- fow: Form of Way (0=undefined, 1=motorway, 2=multiple carriageway, 3=single carriageway, 4=roundabout, 5=traffic square, 6=sliproad)
-- flowdir: Flow direction (1=two-way, 2=one-way end to start, 3=one-way start to end)
